episodes.title: Is JW a CULT? Hear Elle Reno's Horrific Experience! - EX JW - Interview
episodes.description:
"Is JW a CULT? Hear Elle Reno's Horrific Experience! - EX JW - Interview " takes you on a powerful and emotional exploration of life after leaving a high-control group. This video dives deep into the experiences of former Jehovah's Witnesses breaking free from the grip of cults and high-control organizations.

If you’ve recently left the Jehovah's Witnesses or are contemplating leaving a similar group, this video offers encouragement, hope, and practical insights. Discover the challenges Elle faced during the journey of healing from religious trauma, rebuilding a sense of self, and finding freedom.

Learn about common struggles like overcoming the fear of shunning, coping with emotional manipulation, and reclaiming personal autonomy. This video is ideal for ex-Jehovah’s Witnesses, ex-cult members, or anyone seeking information on deprogramming from cults and starting anew.

At Laura X Timber we welcome all people to join the conversation and help those transitioning out of high-control groups.

Don’t miss out—subscribe for more videos on leaving cults, healing journeys, and personal growth. Like, share, and comment to connect with a supportive community of others who understand your experience.

episodes.title: The Ex-Amish Woman Who Became a Missionary
episodes.description:
Discover the inspiring journey of an ex-Amish woman who overcame cultural and religious barriers to embrace a new life as a missionary. In "The Ex-Amish Woman Who Became a Missionary," we dive into her remarkable story of courage, faith, and transformation. This video is a must-watch for anyone curious about leaving the Amish lifestyle or navigating life as an ex-Amish individual.

Learn about the challenges faced when breaking away from the traditional Amish way of life and the steps she took to rebuild her identity. Whether you’re considering leaving the Amish community, adjusting to the outside world, or seeking guidance on starting a fresh chapter, this video offers hope, encouragement, and practical advice.

episodes.title: How I Escaped the IFB Cult - SA Survivor - Amber Interview
episodes.description:
In this eye-opening video, Amber shares her story of growing up in the Independent Fundamental Baptist (IBF) church, and how it has shaped her life.  From the strict rules and regulations to the SA, physical, and emotional abuse. Amber will reveal the dark side of her childhood.  If you're a survivor of a cult experience or are interested in cult recovery, this video is for you. Join Amber as she opens up about her journey and shares her experiences of breaking free from the cult's grasp.

episodes.title: How I Left the Amish Community- Jacob - Ex-Amish Interview
episodes.description:
In this eye-opening interview, Jacob shares his emotional and inspiring story of escaping the Amish community in Canada, where he faced physical abuse and childhood trauma. Having been shunned by the Amish community, Jacob bravely opens up about his experiences, offering a unique insight into the lives of those who have left the Amish. From the struggles of adapting to modern life to the lingering effects of trauma, Jacob's story is a powerful testament to the human spirit. Join us as we delve into the world of the Ex-Amish, and explore the complexities of leaving a community that is often shrouded in mystery.
